casebody.data:
Kelly DEAL
v.
DEPARTMENT OF HOUSING AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT. 17-P-1530 Appeals Court of Massachusetts. Entered: March 1, 2019

The judgment of the Superior Court affirming DHCD's decision is vacated, and a new judgment shall enter vacating DHCD's decision and remanding the case to DHCD for further proceedings consistent with the memorandum and order of the Appeals Court.
